Nigerian hit-making artiste Maleek Berry has released another interesting new single titled “Somebody falling”. Straight out of Berry’s Room, there’s no doubt a lot of fans will definitely fall for this heavy joint delivered by the multi-talented gentleman as expected. However, ‘Somebody Falling‘ serves as his second release for the year, and a good follow-up track to his previously released record ‘Flashy‘. Listen to ‘Somebody Falling” below: 